# .ctxignore — files the ctx hooks leave alone (read/write raw on disk).
# Everything else .md routes through ctx (ctx_search/ctx_read, ctx_write).
# One glob per line; matched against repo-relative and absolute paths.

# Repo + meta files you legitimately read/write directly
README.md
CHANGELOG.md
LICENSE.md
LICENSE
REFONTE.md
source.md
*.example

# Agent harness files the tooling reads directly
**/CLAUDE.md
**/AGENTS.md
.claude/**

# Build / site generators that consume markdown from disk
docs/site/**
